# Thea: iOS Product and Design Guardrails

## Product scope (MVP+)
- Core: list/add/edit/delete/search/sort/status/persistence.
- Next: fermentation progress, ETA, ready state, notes quality, readability.
- Prefer incremental additions; no massive feature bundles.

## UI direction
- Calm premium + natural bio aesthetic.
- Light minimal layout with strong spacing and hierarchy.
- Rounded corners (16-20pt), subtle depth, no heavy borders.
- Use translucent/material cards and soft blur where useful.

## Color system
- Primary green: #4F8A66
- Kombucha yellow: #E6C36A
- Accent amber: #C08A5D
- Background: #F7F7F5
- Text primary: #1C1C1E
- Text secondary: #6B6B6B

## Avoid
- Pure white backgrounds.
- Neon/saturated colors.
- Heavy dark UI and clutter.

## Screen priorities
- Batch List: search, filters, glass cards, quick status scan.
- Batch Detail: key metrics cards, progress ring, notes readability.
- Add/Edit: simple form, clear hierarchy, strong primary action.
